Paper: hep-th/9608149

Date: 1996-08-21

Title: Soldering Chiralities II

Comments: Latex file, 8 pages

We study the non-abelian extension of the soldering process of two chiral WZWmodels of opposite chiralities, resulting in a (non-chiral) WZW model living ina 2D space-time with non trivial Riemanian curvature.